          "bbox": [
            90.0,
            127.10400390625,
            194.67601013183594,
            143.83200073242188
          ],
          "text": "1. Introduction –",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            152.90399169921875,
            552.3411254882812,
            216.60006713867188
          ],
          "text": "The Currency Distribution & Exchange Scheme (CDES) for bank branches including \ncurrency chests has been formulated in order to ensure that all bank branches provide \nbetter customer service to members of public with regard to exchange of notes and coins, \nin keeping with the objectives of Clean Note Policy.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            90.0,
            226.404052734375,
            173.37600708007812,
            243.13204956054688
          ],
          "text": "2. Incentives",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00000762939453,
            252.34803771972656,
            552.3421020507812,
            284.2200622558594
          ],
          "text": "As per the scheme, banks are eligible for the following financial incentives for providing \nfacilities for exchange of notes and coins:",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            80.27999877929688,
            296.4840087890625,
            102.93599700927734,
            327.0119934082031
          ],
          "text": "Sr. \nNo.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
