          "bbox": [
            315.0,
            334.583984375,
            537.937255859375,
            351.3119812011719
          ],
          "text": "a. Capital Cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            86.58000183105469,
            334.6679992675781,
            299.0173034667969,
            398.2799987792969
          ],
          "text": "i) \nOpening \nof \nand \nmaintaining \ncurrency \nchests \nat \ncenters \nhaving population of less than 1 \nlakh in under banked States",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p2_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            315.0,
            350.5679931640625,
            537.9385986328125,
            476.77197265625
          ],
          "text": "50% of capital expenditure subject to \na ceiling of ` 50 lakh per currency \nchest.  In the North Eastern region \nup to 100% of capital expenditure is \neligible for reimbursement subject to \nthe ceiling of ` 50 lakh. \n \nb. Revenue cost: Reimbursement of",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
