            355.9679870605469,
            537.9362182617188,
            435.41998291015625
          ],
          "text": "The maximum amount of reimbursement \nfor the machines will be as follows – \n \nFor Metro / Urban areas –",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
