          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            96.86395263671875,
            378.0398864746094,
            113.59195709228516
          ],
          "text": "3. \nOperational Guidelines to avail the incentives -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            122.72393798828125,
            292.05853271484375,
            139.45193481445312
          ],
          "text": "3.1   \nPerformance based incentives -",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            148.6679229736328,
            552.3399047851562,
            212.27999877929688
          ],
          "text": "i) \nThe incentives will be paid on the soiled notes actually received in the Issue Office \nof the RBI.  Banks need not submit a separate claim in this regard.  Currency chest \nbranch will have to pass on the incentive to the linked branches for the soiled notes \ntendered by them on a pro-rata basis.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00001525878906,
            222.16798400878906,
            552.3384399414062,
            269.8800354003906
          ],
          "text": "ii) \nSimilarly, incentive will be paid in respect of the adjudicated notes received along \nwith the soiled note remittances / sent separately by registered / insured post in a sealed \ncover to the RBI.  No separate claim is required to be made.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.00003051757812,
            279.68402099609375,
            329.37603759765625,
            296.4120178222656
          ],
          "text": "3.2   \nIncentives for installation of machines",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            305.6280212402344,
            552.341064453125,
            385.0799865722656
          ],
          "text": "i)  \nThe banks intending to purchase various machines as also establish currency \nchests during the period from July 01st to June 30th of a year, may submit their Annual \nPlans containing the details of the machines and the cost, to our Issue Offices latest by \nApril 15 of every year on an ongoing basis. Our Issue offices, on receipt of the plans, may \nadvise the maximum amount of reimbursement permissible to each bank for that year.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            72.0,
            394.9679870605469,
            552.3421630859375,
            474.4199523925781
          ],
          "text": "ii) \nThe claims for incentives for installation of Cash Recyclers and ATMs dispensing \nlower denomination notes should be submitted to the respective Issue Office of RBI on \nquarterly basis within 30 days from the close of the respective quarter through the Link \nOffice of the bank concerned.  Such claims may however be submitted only after full \npayment is made to the vendors for the machines.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p4_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            247.08001708984375,
            484.3079528808594,
            377.1960754394531,
            500.2799377441406
          ],
          "text": "___________________",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
